          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1690285221322-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Add the<strong> onion wedges </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges</strong> to one side of a separate baking tray and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
