    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sliced paprika chicken </strong>with the <strong>charred pepper</strong>, <strong>crispy potatoes</strong>, <strong>roasted onion </strong>and <strong>tomato </strong>over the <strong>salad </strong>– this is your<strong> Spanish-style free range chicken & charred pepper salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>spicy aioli </strong>all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
